window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I’m Spencer Whitley, the CEO of a billion-dollar company. But behind closed doors, I’m a clueless, single dad…. Between reading as many parenting books as I can and trying to get the little dude to sleep during the night, I can barely think about anything else.</p> <p>But when I meet my neighbor, my mind begins to wander. Penny is gorgeous and an adorable klutz. After she takes a spill in front of my house, my protective instincts kick <a href=\"http://in.as/\">in.</a></p> <p><a href=\"http://in.as/\">As</a> I bandage up her scrapes, all I want is to get to know her better. Then I watch her play with my son and my defenses start coming down.</p> <p>Suddenly, I keep making up excuses to invite her over. We both have good reasons to be cautious. I want to focus on my son and be a good father. Penny needs a fresh start after a rough break-up. I can’t deny how much I want her, but is this a risk we want to take?</p>"; 
